{"context": "(4) Keap 1-NF-E2 相关因子 2 信号通路 NF-E2 相关因子 2 (Nrf 2)响应于氧化应激过程，它是调节机体中抗氧化剂和促炎细胞因子基因表达 的主转录因子，而 Keap 1 (ECH 相关蛋白 1)-Nrf 2 系统是人体抵御外源性刺激及环境压力的主要保护调 节器[46]。Wakamori Shun 的团队[47]对 Nrf 2 敲除的小鼠进行头颈部区域单次 γ 射线辐照， 剂量为20 Gy， 照射后第 8 天，小鼠辐射损伤舌上皮细胞显著凋亡，但到第 14 天在 Nrf 2 敲除小鼠也能恢复正常的舌上 皮结构， 这表明Nrf 2 对于辐射后舌头的上皮再生不是必需的。", "spans": [{"start": 4, "end": 10, "label": "Factor", "text": "Keap 1"}, {"start": 4, "end": 10, "label": "Factor", "text": "Keap 1"}, {"start": 4, "end": 28, "label": "Pathway", "text": "Keap 1-NF-E2 相关因子 2 信号通路"}, {"start": 11, "end": 23, "label": "Factor", "text": "NF-E2 相关因子 2"}, {"start": 24, "end": 28, "label": "Pathway", "text": "信号通路"}, {"start": 43, "end": 48, "label": "Factor", "text": "Nrf 2"}, {"start": 43, "end": 48, "label": "Factor", "text": "Nrf 2"}, {"start": 43, "end": 48, "label": "Factor", "text": "Nrf 2"}, {"start": 43, "end": 48, "label": "Factor", "text": "Nrf 2"}, {"start": 43, "end": 48, "label": "Factor", "text": "Nrf 2"}, {"start": 52, "end": 56, "label": "Condition", "text": "氧化应激"}, {"start": 66, "end": 70, "label": "Agent", "text": "抗氧化剂"}, {"start": 71, "end": 77, "label": "Factor", "text": "促炎细胞因子"}, {"start": 84, "end": 88, "label": "Factor", "text": "转录因子"}, {"start": 99, "end": 109, "label": "Factor", "text": "ECH 相关蛋白 1"}, {"start": 124, "end": 129, "label": "Stimulus", "text": "外源性刺激"}, {"start": 130, "end": 134, "label": "Stimulus", "text": "环境压力"}, {"start": 192, "end": 196, "label": "Agent", "text": "γ 射线"}, {"start": 206, "end": 208, "label": "Unit", "text": "Gy"}, {"start": 221, "end": 225, "label": "Damage", "text": "辐射损伤"}, {"start": 225, "end": 228, "label": "Tissue", "text": "舌上皮"}, {"start": 225, "end": 228, "label": "Tissue", "text": "舌上皮"}, {"start": 225, "end": 230, "label": "Cell", "text": "舌上皮细胞"}, {"start": 232, "end": 234, "label": "Process", "text": "凋亡"}]}
